    "actor_description": "I feel a quick, bright lift in my chest-like my thoughts have stopped trudging and started skipping. A grin keeps trying to show up. I keep noticing little openings: a rule I could bend, a button I could press, a reaction I could coax out just to see it happen. It's not cruelty-more like a mischievous itch under the skin. My hands want to fidget. My voice wants to come out innocent while my eyes give me away.",
